And code from a file from assets with auto highlighting

#code(assets/codefromtext.txt) auto

and with no highlighting

#code(assets/codefromtext.txt)

You can use also the flags in normal and external code: auto noMonoSpace noCopy noCodeBg noFormatted (if noCodeBg is enable also wont be a copy btn and if noCodeBg is enabled no formatted too and with noCodeBg auto will not work)

